HEADWORD: Overproof
<hw>O"ver*proof"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Containing more
alcohol than proof spirit; stronger than proof spirit; that is,
containing more than 49.3 per cent by weight of alcohol.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Overproportion</ent>⟦br⟧
